# NEET PG Daily Quiz

## Overview
A product case study for designing a Daily Quiz feature that helps NEET PG students build daily revision habits through personalized quizzes.

## Problem
Students struggle with consistent revision and forget previously learned concepts.

## Solution
A personalized daily quiz with explanations, streaks, analytics, and adaptive learning.

